--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
It is a simple application of Banking process. 
The scenario is, Indian bank receiving investments from foreign countries(NRI). 
Here the foreign investors may not aware of their inverstment's equivalence of INR.
The Indian banking personnel also aware only the INR and its interest rate.
Here, this application will be bridge the gap between banking operation and Foreign investments.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Application abstract the money conversion. so the banking personnel no need to worry about the currency type.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sample output:
-------------
The Investment from US NRI in INR =  350000
The Interest gained is =  21000.0
The Investment from Australian NRI in INR =  31800
The Interest gained is =  1908.0
The Investment from Europian NRI in INR =  52000
The Interest gained is =  3120.0
